title: Comedy Nights with Kapil - Sunidhi Chauhan - 28th September - HD
description:
In this episode, Kapil disguises himself as Inspector Shamsher. He keeps telling people about his bravery. He also interacts with public asking their problem against the police. Later, Sunidhi Chauhan comes to the show as the special guest. The audience gets a chance to interact with Sunidhi and sing with her. Watch the complete show to know what happens next. Renowned, actor-comedian Kapil Sharma makes his debut as a TV show producer with his new show Comedy Nights With Kapil. He will be seen multiple roles of an actor, scriptwriter and producer in his production debut. Already famous for his amazing comic timing and his talent to dig humor out of any situation, he is ready present everyday life in a fresh ad unique way.
